00:30:36,740 --> 00:30:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] I samo ono što su malo prije spomenuli,

779
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:42,539
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvati su prisutni u već stoljećima,

780
00:30:42,539 --> 00:30:44,339
[SPEAKER_00] samo neozumno Gecemani

781
00:30:44,339 --> 00:30:47,200
[SPEAKER_00] koji je zbog hrvatskih Hrvata,

782
00:30:47,200 --> 00:30:50,319
[SPEAKER_00] trojice, braće Branković i Sarajeva

783
00:30:50,319 --> 00:30:52,519
[SPEAKER_00] darovali su kustodiju.

784
00:30:52,519 --> 00:30:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda je ono brdo tabor gdje spačava,

785
00:30:54,579 --> 00:30:58,299
[SPEAKER_00] onda ono drvo ispačava

786
00:30:58,299 --> 00:30:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] u krovište,

787
00:30:59,099 --> 00:31:01,220
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda ima toliko vratara

788
00:31:01,220 --> 00:31:03,980
[SPEAKER_00] koji su bili i kustodi ovdje u Svjetoj zemlji

789
00:31:03,980 --> 00:31:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] i povijestičari

790
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] i opet koji su brdo nebo kupili,

791
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,940
[SPEAKER_00] toliko mogli bi nam brajati,

792
00:31:10,940 --> 00:31:14,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je ono prisutstvo naše domovine ovdje.

793
00:31:14,380 --> 00:31:15,759
[SPEAKER_00] Jer mi kao domovina,

794
00:31:15,759 --> 00:31:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] naša domovina ono na nebesima,

795
00:31:18,019 --> 00:31:19,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali ovdje znamo da Isus živio.

796
00:31:19,859 --> 00:31:22,859
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle da jedan počulek dođe u Svjetoj zemlji,

797
00:31:22,859 --> 00:31:23,640
[SPEAKER_00] u zemlju,

798
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] on će shvatiti ove riječi možda malo dubnje,

799
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:27,759
[SPEAKER_00] a sigurno će biti ovdje koji će slušati

800
00:31:28,059 --> 00:31:29,740
[SPEAKER_00] vidjeti ovaj video,

801
00:31:29,740 --> 00:31:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] pa će vidjeti,

802
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:33,599
[SPEAKER_00] pa da, znamo o čemu razgovaraju,

803
00:31:33,599 --> 00:31:34,759
[SPEAKER_00] tamo sam ja to vidio.

804
00:31:36,059 --> 00:31:37,519
[SPEAKER_01] Da, to je živa istina,

805
00:31:37,519 --> 00:31:39,880
[SPEAKER_01] obično kad putujem po svijetu,

806
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:41,599
[SPEAKER_01] onda kažem Hrvatska,

807
00:31:41,599 --> 00:31:42,019
[SPEAKER_01] onda svi,

808
00:31:42,019 --> 00:31:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] a Luka Modrić ili Prijeto,

809
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:44,779
[SPEAKER_01] Vilo Šuker,

810
00:31:44,779 --> 00:31:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] ali u Svjetoj zemlji kad kažeš Hrvatska,

811
00:31:47,420 --> 00:31:47,839
[SPEAKER_01] onda kažu,

812
00:31:47,839 --> 00:31:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] a Buna Sandra.

813
00:31:51,000 --> 00:31:51,920
[SPEAKER_01] vidiš ti da,

814
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:53,960
[SPEAKER_01] a pa to je tako,

815
00:31:53,960 --> 00:31:54,220
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

816
00:31:54,220 --> 00:31:55,819
[SPEAKER_01] nećemo sad uopće,

817
00:31:55,819 --> 00:31:57,819
[SPEAKER_01] tako da evo,

818
00:31:57,819 --> 00:31:58,859
[SPEAKER_01] kad bi Bog imao,

819
00:31:58,859 --> 00:32:02,119
[SPEAKER_01] ili kad bi države imale veleposlanika ljubavi,

820
00:32:02,119 --> 00:32:03,259
[SPEAKER_01] onda bi ti sigurno,

821
00:32:03,259 --> 00:32:04,940
[SPEAKER_01] imao to vijesto,

822
00:32:04,940 --> 00:32:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] jer to u biti,

823
00:32:05,940 --> 00:32:07,920
[SPEAKER_01] u biti u ovom boys homu,

824
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:08,880
[SPEAKER_01] to i je tako,

825
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,700
[SPEAKER_01] ta ljubav je doista življena,

826
00:32:10,700 --> 00:32:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek svako jutro kad se probudim,

827
00:32:12,420 --> 00:32:14,200
[SPEAKER_01] pa krenem kroz vrton,

828
00:32:14,200 --> 00:32:14,759
[SPEAKER_01] da kažem,

829
00:32:14,759 --> 00:32:17,019
[SPEAKER_01] a Sveti Frane bi sad ovdje reka,

830
00:32:17,019 --> 00:32:18,700
[SPEAKER_01] ljubav je ovdje ljubljena,

831
00:32:18,700 --> 00:32:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] i mislim da to zapravo je promjena,

832
00:32:21,539 --> 00:32:23,220
[SPEAKER_01] te paradigme tog osjećaja,

833
00:32:23,220 --> 00:32:24,180
[SPEAKER_01] koji je on imao,

834
00:32:24,180 --> 00:32:26,160
[SPEAKER_01] te žalosti nad Isusovim križom,

835
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:27,720
[SPEAKER_01] da nismo bili sposobni,

836
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:29,400
[SPEAKER_01] kapacitirani ljubiti ljubav,

837
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:31,559
[SPEAKER_01] a sad jednom dođeš na mjesto,

838
00:32:31,559 --> 00:32:33,160
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je doista njegov,

839
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:33,460
[SPEAKER_01] mislim,

840
00:32:33,460 --> 00:32:34,279
[SPEAKER_01] Franji sin,

841
00:32:34,279 --> 00:32:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno ti,

842
00:32:35,059 --> 00:32:36,980
[SPEAKER_01] je onaj koji stvara ambijent,

843
00:32:36,980 --> 00:32:38,220
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem je ljubav ljubljena,

844
00:32:38,220 --> 00:32:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] i to mi je tako divno,

845
00:32:40,039 --> 00:32:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] i to je ono zapravo što te uzme,

846
00:32:41,880 --> 00:32:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] i nekako nahrani,

847
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:45,240
[SPEAKER_01] i imaš osjećaj da ćeš od toga moći odlomiti,

848
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:47,019
[SPEAKER_01] dati taj kruh drugim ljudima,

849
00:32:47,019 --> 00:32:48,799
[SPEAKER_01] koji su sretneš,

850
00:32:48,799 --> 00:32:49,200
[SPEAKER_01] tako da,

851
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,140
[SPEAKER_01] hvala na tome.

852
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:51,200
[SPEAKER_01] Ali evo,

853
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,720
[SPEAKER_01] sad bih htjela još nešto,

854
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:55,559
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi su jako u Hrvatskoj prestrašani,

855
00:32:55,559 --> 00:32:56,220
[SPEAKER_01] i općenito,

856
00:32:56,220 --> 00:32:59,980
[SPEAKER_01] zapadni svijet je pod medijskim terorom,

857
00:32:59,980 --> 00:33:01,180
[SPEAKER_01] ja bih se usudila reći,

858
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:03,220
[SPEAKER_01] i bez ikakvih političkih konotacija,

859
00:33:03,220 --> 00:33:06,319
[SPEAKER_01] želim samo razgovarati o situaciji u Svetoj zemlji,

860
00:33:06,319 --> 00:33:07,480
[SPEAKER_01] jako puno ljudi je,

861
00:33:10,039 --> 00:33:12,339
[SPEAKER_01] i prvi koji je bio za uskrsi ovaj sada,

862
00:33:12,339 --> 00:33:13,099
[SPEAKER_01] malo duži,

863
00:33:13,099 --> 00:33:16,059
[SPEAKER_01] su ili jako prestrašeni,

864
00:33:16,059 --> 00:33:16,460
[SPEAKER_01] i rekli,

865
00:33:16,460 --> 00:33:19,559
[SPEAKER_01] sad nije vrijeme zaputovati u Svetu zemlju,

866
00:33:19,559 --> 00:33:22,359
[SPEAKER_01] a cijelo vrijeme čujemo pozive

867
00:33:22,359 --> 00:33:25,480
[SPEAKER_01] i od prekrasnog ovdje patrijarha,

868
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:28,400
[SPEAKER_01] latinskog Pierbatiste Pizzabale,

869
00:33:28,400 --> 00:33:31,339
[SPEAKER_01] koji stalno poziva kršane da dođu u Svetu zemlju,

870
00:33:31,339 --> 00:33:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] jer većina ljudi ovdje ipak na direktan ili indirektan način,

871
00:33:35,279 --> 00:33:36,759
[SPEAKER_01] osobito na zapadne ovali,

872
00:33:36,759 --> 00:33:38,420
[SPEAKER_01] živi od turizma,

873
00:33:38,539 --> 00:33:41,099
[SPEAKER_01] ili od prodaje, od suvenira, hotela,

874
00:33:41,099 --> 00:33:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] različiti uvostiteljskih usluga,

875
00:33:44,460 --> 00:33:46,200
[SPEAKER_01] i naravno već godinu i koliko,

876
00:33:46,200 --> 00:33:47,660
[SPEAKER_01] dva, tri mjeseca u biti,

877
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:50,700
[SPEAKER_01] to izostaje i ljudima je jako teško.

878
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:51,160
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo,

879
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:54,660
[SPEAKER_01] iz tvoje perspektive nekoga ko živio u stvarnost,

880
00:33:54,660 --> 00:33:56,319
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam tu ipak kraće,

881
00:33:56,319 --> 00:33:58,640
[SPEAKER_01] koji su temeljni problemi,

882
00:33:59,279 --> 00:34:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] kako se može zaustaviti odlazak ljudi Arapa kršena iz ovog dijela svijeta sada ovim teškim okolnostima,

883
00:34:06,940 --> 00:34:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] jer znamo to po hrvatskom modelu, ljudi kada odu jako se teško vraćaju.

884
00:34:12,159 --> 00:34:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] I što bi bila tvoja poruka Hrvatima,

885
00:34:14,659 --> 00:34:16,400
[SPEAKER_01] znači našim ljudima u domovini,

886
00:34:16,400 --> 00:34:18,619
[SPEAKER_01] kako bi trebali imati odnosi,

887
00:34:18,619 --> 00:34:21,019
[SPEAKER_01] i evo, slobodno ih možeš pozvati da se ohrabre,

888
00:34:21,019 --> 00:34:21,559
[SPEAKER_01] da dođe,

889
00:34:21,559 --> 00:34:25,320
[SPEAKER_01] ja mogu posvjedoći da ne postoji nijedna kulisa,

890
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:27,239
[SPEAKER_01] koja može bi alternativa miru,

891
00:34:27,239 --> 00:34:29,280
[SPEAKER_01] koji mi ovdje zapravo živimo,

892
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] Prva stvar,

893
00:34:33,039 --> 00:34:35,260
[SPEAKER_00] evo, u ovih godine,

894
00:34:35,260 --> 00:34:37,900
[SPEAKER_00] par mjeseci i koliko je ovo traje ovaj rat i tako,

895
00:34:37,900 --> 00:34:40,179
[SPEAKER_00] nije bila trenutka da

896
00:34:40,179 --> 00:34:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] hodočasnici su bile nekoj opasnosti.

897
00:34:43,500 --> 00:34:45,019
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

898
00:34:45,019 --> 00:34:47,400
[SPEAKER_00] Grupe od početaka samih

899
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:49,860
[SPEAKER_00] nisu prestajale dolaziti.

900
00:34:49,860 --> 00:34:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno, možda iz Europa manje,

901
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:53,260
[SPEAKER_00] iz Europe dolaze,

902
00:34:53,260 --> 00:34:54,739
[SPEAKER_00] ali ne toliko kao ora prije.

903
00:34:54,739 --> 00:34:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, hvala Bogu,

904
00:34:56,639 --> 00:34:58,679
[SPEAKER_00] sad ima dobrih pomaka i naznaka.

905
00:34:59,280 --> 00:35:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] od početka ovog mjeseca

906
00:35:01,559 --> 00:35:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] do biti sredine,

907
00:35:02,539 --> 00:35:05,159
[SPEAKER_00] puno tih zrakopalovih kompanija

908
00:35:05,159 --> 00:35:05,960
[SPEAKER_00] se vraćaju.

909
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] Prva stvar, druga stvar,

910
00:35:08,340 --> 00:35:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] naravno da je mediji to malo na bušu.

911
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] Puno puta sam ja to rekao

912
00:35:13,480 --> 00:35:14,099
[SPEAKER_00] od početaka,

913
00:35:14,099 --> 00:35:15,840
[SPEAKER_00] kada su evo neke medijske kuće

914
00:35:15,840 --> 00:35:17,320
[SPEAKER_00] mene zpitali iz izjeva,

915
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:17,920
[SPEAKER_00] sam rekao,

916
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,019
[SPEAKER_00] nemojte se bojati,

917
00:35:19,019 --> 00:35:19,880
[SPEAKER_00] dođete uvijek.

918
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:22,260
[SPEAKER_00] Nije tako uvijek kao što je

919
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:24,079
[SPEAKER_00] vidite na televiziji i u medijima.

920
00:35:24,079 --> 00:35:25,059
[SPEAKER_00] Nije sve tako.

921
00:35:25,059 --> 00:35:26,179
[SPEAKER_00] Svi znamo da je,

922
00:35:26,179 --> 00:35:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] svi znamo iz prve ruke

923
00:35:27,619 --> 00:35:28,599
[SPEAKER_00] koliko puta vidiš

924
00:35:28,599 --> 00:35:29,360
[SPEAKER_00] jednu vijest.

925
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:30,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ti kad si na terenu,

926
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] nekada je što te lizi,

927
00:35:31,739 --> 00:35:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] da su to dvije

928
00:35:33,019 --> 00:35:36,219
[SPEAKER_00] proporcionalne stvari.

929
00:35:36,219 --> 00:35:39,659
[SPEAKER_00] Nemaju ovoga

930
00:35:39,659 --> 00:35:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] jedne veze,

931
00:35:40,900 --> 00:35:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] jedna s drugom.

932
00:35:41,579 --> 00:35:43,400
[SPEAKER_00] A naravno,

933
00:35:43,400 --> 00:35:46,780
[SPEAKER_00] kao tako,

934
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:47,760
[SPEAKER_00] na taj način,

935
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:49,420
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo sada,

936
00:35:49,420 --> 00:35:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] kad čovjek dođe,

937
00:35:50,300 --> 00:35:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] može ostati na svjetim mjestima

938
00:35:51,500 --> 00:35:51,960
[SPEAKER_00] i duže.

939
00:35:51,960 --> 00:35:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nemo na trčanja,

940
00:35:53,559 --> 00:35:54,599
[SPEAKER_00] vakacijona,

941
00:35:54,599 --> 00:35:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] naput moraju posjediti

942
00:35:55,980 --> 00:35:58,099
[SPEAKER_00] ajmo idemo dalje.

943
00:35:58,159 --> 00:35:58,280
[SPEAKER_00] ne.

944
00:35:58,280 --> 00:35:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] Sada se čovjek može zaustaviti,

945
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:01,980
[SPEAKER_00] može doista meditirati

946
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] i kontaklirati na tim mjestima.

947
00:36:03,559 --> 00:36:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] To je velika,

948
00:36:04,119 --> 00:36:04,820
[SPEAKER_00] velika stvar.

949
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:06,639
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da evo,

950
00:36:06,639 --> 00:36:07,800
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvati kao takvi

951
00:36:07,800 --> 00:36:09,280
[SPEAKER_00] dolaze.

952
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ako Bog dao,

953
00:36:10,219 --> 00:36:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] treće mjesece,

954
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] bit će hodočašće.

955
00:36:12,159 --> 00:36:13,719
[SPEAKER_00] Otvorenje naša kapelica

956
00:36:13,719 --> 00:36:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje u Betlehemu,

957
00:36:14,400 --> 00:36:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] koja je predivna,

958
00:36:15,900 --> 00:36:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] koja je već sada poznata.

959
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:19,219
[SPEAKER_00] tako da evo,

960
00:36:19,219 --> 00:36:20,320
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi su već,

961
00:36:20,320 --> 00:36:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] odmah se popunio avion,

962
00:36:21,679 --> 00:36:22,780
[SPEAKER_00] čarter dolaze

963
00:36:22,780 --> 00:36:25,300
[SPEAKER_00] i to je sigurno već sada,

964
00:36:25,300 --> 00:36:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

965
00:36:25,940 --> 00:36:26,800
[SPEAKER_00] bit će jedan naznak

966
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] kad ljudima kažu,

967
00:36:27,679 --> 00:36:28,880
[SPEAKER_00] kad vide iz prve ruke,

968
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] onda će joj reći,

969
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] e pa da,

970
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:31,559
[SPEAKER_00] stvarno je dobro,

971
00:36:31,559 --> 00:36:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] dođite.

972
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:34,780
[SPEAKER_00] ne treba se bojati.

973
00:36:34,780 --> 00:36:35,880
[SPEAKER_00] Naš kustod iso tako

974
00:36:35,880 --> 00:36:37,460
[SPEAKER_00] uz Patriarha pozvao

975
00:36:37,460 --> 00:36:38,480
[SPEAKER_00] na ovaj časni

976
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:39,199
[SPEAKER_00] kada dođu

977
00:36:39,199 --> 00:36:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] i evo,

978
00:36:40,739 --> 00:36:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] ti si vidjela

979
00:36:41,480 --> 00:36:42,360
[SPEAKER_00] ovih dana

980
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] da stvarno nije bilo

981
00:36:43,420 --> 00:36:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] problema

982
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:45,340
